  "description": "<p>分类: <a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/category/software-apps/\" rel=\"tag\">软件应用</a></p><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2014/03/24/tumblr-two-step-authentication/\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://o.aolcdn.com/hss/storage/adam/b38e57c3c20884b4ca5ed5792b398e3d/tumblr-two-step-verification.jpg\" style=\"width: 620px; height: 290px;\" /></a></div>\n\n<div><br />\n两步验证正越来越受到网络服务商的重视，而最新加入这项功能的就是 <a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/tag/tumblr\">Tumblr</a> 了。他们今天在自己的博客中宣布，未来他们将会为用户提供基于短信或应用（类似 Google 的 Authenticator）的账户两步验证功能，用户需要输入相应的验证码后才能使用服务，这样其数据便会更加安全。按照官方的说法，验证过程不会影响到行动端的使用，你只需在账户设定页面中设定一个一次性的密码，之后在设备上输入就可以了。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n经由：<a href=\"http://www.engadget.com/2014/03/24/tumblr-two-step-authentication/\">Engadget</a>、<span class=\"via\"><a href=\"http://techcrunch.com/2014/03/24/tumblr-gets-more-secure-with-addition-of-two-factor-authentication/\" target=\"_blank\">TechCrunch</a></span><br />\n引用来源：<span class=\"source\"><a href=\"http://www.tumblr.com/docs/en/two_factor_auth\" target=\"_blank\">Tumblr (1)</a></span>、<span class=\"source\"><a href=\"http://staff.tumblr.com/post/80583764030/the-smile-of-a-loved-one-your-childhood-blanket\" target=\"_blank\">(2)</a></span></div><p><h6 style=\"clear: both; padding: 8px 0 0 0; height: 2px; font-size: 1px; border: 0; margin: 0; padding: 0;\"></h6><a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2014/03/24/tumblr-two-step-authentication/\" rel=\"bookmark\" title=\"Permanent link to this entry\">此文章网址</a>&nbsp;|&nbsp;<a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/forward/20855634/\" title=\"Send this entry to a friend via email\">转寄此文章</a>&nbsp;|&nbsp;<a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2014/03/24/tumblr-two-step-authentication/#comments\" title=\"View reader comments on this entry\">回应</a><hr size=\"1\" />", 
